{"tid":1782673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗稱林鄭月娥周一會與習近平會面　將作公開交代","createTime":"2019-12-14T07:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T10:20:16.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"686ffa6d509d771a81accd5372fd646d2e24b508","tid":1782673,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:17:11.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥今日起到北京述職4日，政務司司長張建宗表示，林鄭月娥將會在星期一與國家主席習近平會面，相信林鄭月娥會在會面作公開交代。他表示，政府會繼續努力施政，有決心面對挑戰，有信心會走出困局。<br />\n<br />\n對於中美就首階段經貿協議文本達成一致，張建宗形容是喜事、好事，但要視乎落實的情況如何。他說，中美貿易糾紛不單影響中美兩國，亦影響全球，雖然香港是單獨關稅區，但相信會在今次事件中受惠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497655-20191214.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497655-20191214.htm&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGICPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=47a72d15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497655-20191214.htm&h=ab282b69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497655-20191214.htm</a>"},{"pid":"421d1139ecaa159138af7e98981d5d03eee42fd9","tid":1782673,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:17:37.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aca04d7a4c3a055ae2e853769008af58ae27de8c","tid":1782673,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:18:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3847970a90e80da7a88486a92b69e8b7d87ec46","tid":1782673,"uid":261913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:19:01.000Z","msg":"你話佢兩個唔係有路都無人信啦<br />\n咁短時間又見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fa618bf2ded9eec52ec374df02903932abc6ff","tid":1782673,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"